== Testing ==
* all unit tests have to pass for a release
* setting BasDeM up on a fresh system
* upgrade an existing installation

== Announcement ==
* don't forget to include all security related fixes
* major bugfixes
* major features
* download link including checksum
* ChangeLog link

== Tarball ==
* once testing is finished create a tag for the new version
* create a tarball from that tag
* run the tests again, using that tarball!

